    "# XKCD your Brain\n",
    "This Script (that is not perfect) downloads and imports XKCD comics into your brain.\n",
    "\n",
    "Some will fail to complete, and I haven't investigated why. 2215 and 2222, for example, have issues with the images.\n",
    "\n",
    "Create a single thought called `xkcd`. Set your comic range on Cell 5. Run all steps. It might be a good idea to do small batches. "
   ]
